---
title: FathomDB 0.8.2 — M1 multi-hop answer-accuracy harness (design + pre-registration)
status: decision-ready
date: 2026-06-16
owner: 0.8.2 Slice 0 (design-adr)
binds: dev/plans/plan-0.8.2.md §4 (Slice 0 contract), dev/roadmap/0.8.2.md §3
supersedes-instrument-gap: dev/plans/runs/0.8.1-beat-bm25-report.md (narrow recall negative)
